parameters:
\SE[90]No, no... What are you doing? We're in the middle of
a serious audience here.

\SE[95]I lost.... to the Yuri Hime-style Strawberry
Parfait.... \SE[51]We succumbed to its overwhelming
temptation....

\SE\SE[43]Yuri Hime-style Strawberry Parfait...! It exists,
huh...!! \SE[43]That can't be helped! I've been defeated by
it in the past too!
\SE[8] I ate too much... It's all Laura's fault...

\SE[95]I-I'm sorry...! \SE[31]While everyone is working so
hard, as your lover, I shouldn't be behaving
inappropriately...!

\SE[24]Ahh... Laura... My stomach has become so big, like
that of a pregnant woman...

\SE[47]My stomach is so round... It's cute.... \SE[46]Oh no,
it feels like a new door is about to open...

\SE[2]Let's ask the chef for an additional dessert.
\SE[51]Ah... I want to see more of you...! It makes me so
excited...!!

\SE[74]Geez... Even though it's supposed to be a decisive
battle next, there's absolutely no sense of tension...

\SE\SE[3]Rather than being too stiff...! \SE[3]Since both of
you are big shots! \.With this level, it's just a ripple
feeling!

Laura...! They have a 'Crab Cream Cold Pasta'...! With this,
the absorption will be good, so it will quickly turn into
fat!

Wait... Are you really going to eat it?! I don't want to get
fat. Is that okay...?!

I will show you that I can love you no matter what form you
take. This is also a 'challenge' for myself. It will also
serve as proof of my love for you...!

\SE[38]Hmm... My stomach is starting to feel good. They
mentioned something about a Crab Cream Cold Pasta....
\SE[69]It would be the perfect dish to satisfy my hunger....

\SE[74]As you said, I'm starting to feel like we have a big
shot lineup...
